work.work-title: Angels from the realms of glory

credit.credit-words: Shepherds, in the field abiding, Watching o'er your flocks by night, God with us is now residing; Yonder shines the infant light:
Come and worship, come and worship, Worship Christ, the newborn King.
Angels from the realms of glory
Saints, before the altar bending, Watching long in hope and fear; Suddenly the Lord, descending, In His temple shall appear.
